---

const ResumeLink = '/images/BottegaFullStack2024-FS-Certificado-CE.png'; // Link to your blog post
---

<p class="mt-5 animate">
  Here are the technologies I specialize in! This is just a glimpse of my
  expertise. <br />
  <strong> For a detailed overview, here is the Certificate from Bottega University. </strong>
</p>

<div class="mt-4 flex gap-4 animate">
  <a href={ResumeLink} target="/images/BottegaFullStack2024-FS-Certificado-CE.pdf" class="btn btn-download">Bottega University Certificate</a>
    <img class="logoBottega" src="/images/Bottegalogo.png "height="50" width="100" alt="Bottega Logo">
  
</div>

<style>
  .grid-container {
    width: 100%;
    height: 500px;
  }

  .btn {
    @apply inline-block font-bold no-underline px-4 py-2 rounded-md shadow-lg transition-transform duration-300 ease-in-out;
    color: white;
  }

  .btn-download {
    background-color: var(--clr-rose);
    box-shadow:
      0 10px 20px rgba(225, 29, 72, 0.5),
      0 6px 6px rgba(225, 29, 72, 0.5),
      0 0 100px -10px var(--clr-rose);
  }

  .btn-download:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow:
      0 14px 28px rgba(225, 29, 72, 0.25),
      0 10px 10px rgba(225, 29, 72, 0.22),
      0 0 120px -10px var(--clr-rose);
  }

  .btn-blog {
    background-color: var(--clr-purple);
    box-shadow:
      0 10px 20px rgba(106, 13, 173, 0.5),
      0 6px 6px rgba(106, 13, 173, 0.5),
      0 0 100px -10px var(--clr-purple);
  }

  .btn-blog:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow:
      0 14px 28px rgba(106, 13, 173, 0.25),
      0 10px 10px rgba(106, 13, 173, 0.22),
      0 0 120px -10px var(--clr-c);
  }

  .btn-blog {
    color: white;
  }
</style>
